      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies, with the dual-VANOS system recently serviced for optimal cam timing. The chassis has been addressed for common platform weaknesses, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated trailing arm bushings to maintain precise toe alignment under load. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with mechanical certainty, paired with a functional M-variable differential lock for superior exit traction. Maintenance is up to date with a recent valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing prophylaxis. This is a high-performance specimen optimized for tactile feedback and cornering kinematics.",
